author: The Current
description:
Watch Soccer Mommy (Sophie Allison) play "Lost" at The Current
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube or hit the Thanks button

Sophie Allison, best known by the musical moniker Soccer Mommy, released her latest album, 'Evergreen,' in October 2024. While on tour in support of the album, Soccer Mommy visited The Current to play solo versions of a couple songs from the new record along with one from her 2018 debut album, 'Clean.'

Watch and listen a performance of "Lost" above.

Musician
Sophia Allison – guitar, vocals
